OL,3,CBowls club struggling to pay massive
OL,4,C900% hike in standing charges
OL,6,FA bowls club in Bexhill-on-Sea is
OL,7,Ffighting an eye-watering 900% increase
OL,8,Fin its energy bill.
OL,10,FEgerton Park Indoor Bowls Club has
OL,11,Fbeen told the standing charge it needs
OL,12,Fto pay has risen from #25 a month to
OL,13,F#250 a month.
OL,15,FThe energy regulator said it's
OL,16,Fspeaking to the supplier over the
OL,17,Fhike, but the club is having to foot
OL,18,Fthe bill or risk being disconnected.
