OL,3,CBowls club struggling to pay massive
OL,4,C900% hike in standing charges
OL,6,FChairman of the club, Dennis Parkinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "It has been extremely
OL,8,Ffrustrating because there doesn't seem
OL,9,Fto be anyone you can go to to give
OL,10,Fyou, I wouldn't say independent advice.
OL,12,F"Everyone has said it's just
OL,13,Fridiculous.
OL,15,F"We have a sports club 14 miles from
OL,16,Fhere, Eastbourne Sports Club, exactly
OL,17,Fthe same size as this, run the same
OL,18,Famount of power within, and they pay
OL,19,F45p a day, #14 a month.
