OL,3,CBowls club struggling to pay massive
OL,4,C900% hike in standing charges
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, we're stuck with this
OL,7,Fhuge price increase which is not
OL,8,Fjustified in our opinion.
OL,10,F"We just want to run the club and get
OL,11,Fon with looking after the club..
OL,13,F"We shouldn't be dealing with matters
OL,14,Flike this and there should be another
OL,15,Fway.
OL,17,F"I just thought I had the decimal
OL,18,Fpoint in the wrong place and that was
OL,19,Fwhat I suggested initially."
