OL,6,FA DESNZ spokesperson said: "These
OL,7,Fallegations are highly concerning and
OL,8,FOfgem are looking at the issue.
OL,10,F"We are taking action to fix the
OL,11,Fbroken energy market by strengthening
OL,12,Fthe Energy Ombudsman and driving up
OL,13,Fstandards, and have consulted on
OL,14,Fregulation of third-party
OL,15,Fintermediaries, including brokers.
OL,17,F"We will ensure complaints are
OL,18,Fresolved quickly and protect consumers
OL,19,Fwith fairer, quicker and easier access
OL,20,Fto compensation when their supplier
OL,21,Ffalls short."
