OL,4,C900% hike in standing charges
OL,6,FAn Ofgem spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Protecting both domestic and non-
OL,8,Fdomestic consumers is our top
OL,9,Fpriority, and we continuously monitor
OL,10,Fsuppliers to make sure they follow our
OL,11,Frules.
OL,13,F"Standing charges, which cover the
OL,14,Ffixed cost of powering our homes and
OL,15,Fbusinesses, can vary. But we expect
OL,16,Fsuppliers to be transparent with their
OL,17,Fcustomers about what charges include,
OL,18,Fand to explain any changes clearly.
